author: Justin Zaremba | NJ Advance Media for NJ.com
title: Longtime GOP congressmen attracting a growing number of protesters and baked goods
text: Constituents from the 7th and 11th congressional districts are seeking face-to-face meetings with U.S. Rep. Leonard Lance and U.S. Rep. Rodney Frelinghuysen, respectively.
